cross: Cymbidium Pink Champagne x Cymbidum Red Beauty

measurements.description: Eighty-five flowers and nine buds on eight erect inflorescences well presented above foliage; five pseudobulbs, 160-cm diameter, 106-cm tall plant grown in a 20-cm round plastic pot; sepals and petals cream, suffused dark rose, linear spots, burgundy central lines; lip white, bugundy spots, midlobe edged burgundy apically; substance firm; texture matte.
